options processing depends on whether loadPackage is used, which is unfortunate:

    i1 : loadPackage "Foo"
    OptionTable

    o1 = Foo

    o1 : Package

    i3 : load "Foo.m2"
    List

    i4 : get "Foo.m2"

    o4 = newPackage ( "Foo", Configuration => {} )
	 print class (options Foo).Configuration

